{"title":"一盒口罩卖一千！有人在抗疫一线奋战，有人却在发“口罩财”！","date":"2020-01-22T02:30:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 22, 2020","L":"01/22/2020","MM-DD":"01-22"},"link":"2020/01/22/FC-MaskOverPrice","comments":true,"tags":["事实核查"],"categories":["事实核查"],"updated":"2021-08-08T16:27:18.741Z","content":"<h2 id=\"核查背景\">核查背景<a title=\"#核查背景\" href=\"#核查背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>近日国内爆发新型肺炎，根据人民日报官方微博1月22日最新微博的消息：新型肺炎目前确诊440例，死亡9例。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/CtSeHMwOabxLKY6.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>1月21日人民日报官方微博发布了题为《多科权威专家：春运如何严防新型冠状病毒》的文章，提到佩戴N95/医用外壳口罩能够预防新型冠状病毒。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/cpf28Kg3BjnMlxT.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>到1月22日10：46**#N95口罩**话题登到微博热搜第六名。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/D5SAwlrLIa8P1gi.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>话题下是一条*@北京晚报* 发布的题目为《一盒<em>口罩</em>卖一千！有人在抗疫一线奋战，有人却在发“<em>口罩</em>财”！》的微博。本文将对该条微博进行事实核查。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/Wxd2LroqySXpsjc.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"事实点列举\">事实点列举<a title=\"#事实点列举\" href=\"#事实点列举\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>某些电商平台销售的口罩明显涨价</li>\n<li>不少店家的N95口罩从原价99元涨到三四百至上千</li>\n<li>多个电商平台3M品牌旗舰店内KN95及KN90口罩均出现断货情况</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p>本文将对以上三点分别进行核查。</p>\n<h2 id=\"事实核查\">事实核查<a title=\"#事实核查\" href=\"#事实核查\"></a></h2>\n<p>本文采用网上找到的<a href=\"http://www.lsjgcx.com/\" target=\"_blank\">历史价格查询工具</a></p>\n<p>以口罩为关键词，销量从高到低排列对京东淘宝排名前位的口罩商品的历史价格进行查询，结果如下。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>京东部分商品：</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/ZSXFkwVeHItPGyl.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3a%2f%2fitem.jd.com%2f1306182.html%23none\" target=\"_blank\">http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.jd.com%2F1306182.html%23none</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/6chfXuYKsdoSL7v.png\" alt=\"image-20200122110710544.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.jd.com%2F3649920.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.jd.com%2F3649920.html</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/FeEnVdcIpk94BhS.png\" alt=\"image-20200122110804819.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.jd.com%2F3500471.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.jd.com%2F3500471.html</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/dDmGQv6fXiARlCM.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.jd.com%2F4979082.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.jd.com%2F4979082.html</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>淘宝部分商品：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/GIz8VSgJqMkyh9U.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.taobao.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fid%3D539796289435\" target=\"_blank\">http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.taobao.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fid%3D539796289435</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/zUEA2ljcQBNoxYk.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.yao.95095.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.8.66e833c04lscW5%26id%3D599648775985%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D5\" target=\"_blank\">http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.yao.95095.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.8.66e833c04lscW5%26id%3D599648775985%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D5</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/FH6z5cvskDbfNCh.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.9.1b41586e8B8J9X%26id%3D535488579227%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D5\" target=\"_blank\">http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.9.1b41586e8B8J9X%26id%3D535488579227%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D5</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/FH6z5cvskDbfNCh.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?id=580750137136&amp;skuId=4307905657713\" target=\"_blank\">https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?id=580750137136&amp;skuId=4307905657713</a></p>\n<p>从结果来看，有部分商品短期内涨价<strong>事实点1部分准确</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"事实点2\">事实点2<a title=\"#事实点2\" href=\"#事实点2\"></a></h3>\n<p>事实点2中本身描述有误。从99元上涨到到三四百至上千，并未提及数量，也就是商品具体的单价。</p>\n<p>按照原文中图片关键词在天猫搜索，已找不到原商品。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/kcAXDnjdRMvrGfY.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>上图为本文作者于天猫的搜索结果，下路为文章中的配图</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/6jp2N8SeECUfmFA.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>对检索结果出现的商品进行历史价格核查，发现为今日刚刚上架的商品<br>\n<img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/rdZajMfcGyq2BzI.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<a href=\"http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.7.38564853DQk82f%26id%3D607376168621%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D5\" target=\"_blank\">http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.7.38564853DQk82f%26id%3D607376168621%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D5</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/hk2luZCJa1eroM6.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<a href=\"http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.19.38564853DQk82f%26id%3D520117280131%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D5\" target=\"_blank\">http://p.zwjhl.com/price.aspx?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.19.38564853DQk82f%26id%3D520117280131%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D5</a></p>\n<p>小结：<strong>因原商品均已下架，无法核查。但原文中没有提及单价和商品类别，只描述价格的上涨，本身的逻辑有误。</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"事实点3\">事实点3<a title=\"#事实点3\" href=\"#事实点3\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>3M天猫旗舰店中在售的N95、N90口罩均已售空<br>\n<img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/koArDRcpPvG2LQM.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/Yf56bphMkTAX2u4.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>3M京东旗舰店中在售的N95、N90口罩上海地区、北京地区等均无货<br>\n<img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/22/LDJz2y59Gql8h1e.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>从天猫和京东两大电商平台来看，事实点3描述准确</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"核查结果\">核查结果<a title=\"#核查结果\" href=\"#核查结果\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>某些电商平台销售的口罩明显涨价——部分准确</li>\n<li>不少店家的N95口罩从原价99元涨到三四百至上千——无法核查</li>\n<li>多个电商平台3M品牌旗舰店内KN95及KN90口罩均出现断货情况——情况属实</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>我们未能找到已下架商品的具体价格信息，但电商平台只有部分口罩涨价，且原文本身说法有误，有诱导嫌疑。多个电商平台3M品牌旗舰店在售KN95/KN90口罩均断货的说法属实。</strong></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Promises第七章","link":"2020/01/22/PromisesChapter7"},"next":{"title":"Promises第六章","link":"2020/01/22/PromisesChapter6"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/01/22/FC-MaskOverPrice/","toc":[{"id":"核查背景","title":"核查背景","index":"1"},{"id":"事实点列举","title":"事实点列举","index":"2"},{"id":"事实核查","title":"事实核查","index":"3","children":[{"id":"事实点2","title":"事实点2","index":"3.1"},{"id":"事实点3","title":"事实点3","index":"3.2"}]},{"id":"核查结果","title":"核查结果","index":"4"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"August 9, 2021"},"reading_time":"1160 words in 8 min"}